@baseUrl = http://localhost:5095

### 1. Check initial wallet balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/balance

### 2. Check active races
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/races/active

### 3. Place a bet on the first available race odds
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets/place-bet
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "totalStake": 10.0,
  "bets": [
    {
      "raceOddsId": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 4. Check wallet balance after bet (should be reduced)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/balance

### 5. Wait for races to finish and tickets to be processed by background service
### Then check wallet balance again (should show payout if bet won)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/balance

### 6. Check configuration
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/configuration
